  "在处理函数里加一个 int times 参数，它会从 ?times= 绑定。": "Add an int times parameter to the handler; it binds from ?times=.",
  "参数绑定的两条来源": "Two sources of parameter binding",
  "Minimal API 看处理函数的参数名来决定怎么填值。如果参数名出现在路径模板的 {} 里，就从路径段取；否则对简单类型（string、int 等）默认从查询字符串取。所以 \"/hello/{name}\" 配 string name 是路由绑定，而 int times 没出现在路径里，就成了查询参数。": "Minimal API inspects handler parameter names to decide how to fill them. If the name appears inside {} in the route template, it comes from the path segment; otherwise simple types (string, int, etc.) default to the query string. So \"/hello/{name}\" with string name is route binding, while int times absent from the path becomes a query parameter.",
  "name 来自路径，times 来自查询字符串": "name from the path, times from the query string",
