  "类型与可选值": "Types and optional values",
  "声明成 int times 时这个查询参数是必填的，缺了会返回 400。想让它可选并带默认值，写 int times = 1；想允许它不存在，写 int? times（可空类型）。框架会自动把字符串 \"3\" 转成 int，转换失败也返回 400，你不必手写解析。": "Declaring int times makes the query parameter required; omitting it returns 400. To make it optional with a default, write int times = 1; to allow absence, write int? times (nullable). The framework converts the string \"3\" to int automatically and returns 400 on failure, so you never parse by hand.",
  "别把必填查询参数当成可有可无——线上少传一个 times 就会变成 400，而不是用默认值。": "Don't treat a required query parameter as optional; a missing times in production becomes a 400, not a default.",
