  "返回对象就是返回 JSON": "Returning an object means returning JSON",
  "上一课返回字符串得到 text/plain。这一课返回一个对象（或对象数组），Minimal API 会用 System.Text.Json 把它序列化成 JSON，并把响应头 Content-Type 设为 application/json，状态码默认 200。你完全不用手动调用序列化器。": "Last lesson, returning a string gave text/plain. Here, returning an object (or array of objects) makes Minimal API serialize it to JSON with System.Text.Json, set Content-Type to application/json, and default the status to 200. You never call the serializer yourself.",
  "record 数组被自动序列化为 JSON 数组": "An array of records auto-serializes to a JSON array",
  "record 自带按值比较和简洁构造，非常适合做 API 的数据传输对象（DTO）。": "Records come with value equality and concise constructors, ideal as API DTOs.",
  "用 Results 控制状态码": "Control status codes with Results",
  "直接返回对象只能表达 200。真实接口还要表达 404、400、201。Results 工厂方法解决这个问题：Results.Ok(x) 返回 200 带 JSON 体，Results.NotFound() 返回 404，Results.Created(uri, x) 返回 201。它们都实现 IResult，所以当处理函数里出现多条返回分支时，把它声明成返回 IResult。": "Returning an object only expresses 200. Real APIs also need 404, 400, 201. The Results factory methods solve this: Results.Ok(x) returns 200 with a JSON body, Results.NotFound() returns 404, Results.Created(uri, x) returns 201. They all implement IResult, so when a handler has multiple return branches, declare it to return IResult.",
  "找到返回 200+JSON，找不到返回 404": "Found returns 200+JSON, missing returns 404",
  "两条分支返回不同 IResult 时别用 var 接住——lambda 推断不出统一类型会编译失败，要么显式写 IResult，要么用三元表达式。": "When two branches return different IResults, don't capture with var; the lambda can't infer a common type and won't compile. Use an explicit IResult or a ternary expression.",
  "整合：POST 创建资源": "Integration: POST to create a resource",
  "创建": "Create",
  "用 MapPost 接收 JSON 请求体绑定成对象，加入内存集合，并用 Results.Created 返回 201 和 Location。": "Use MapPost to bind a JSON request body to an object, add it to an in-memory list, and return 201 with a Location via Results.Created.",
  "MapPost 的处理函数参数若是复杂类型（如 Product），框架默认从请求体读 JSON 并反序列化。": "If a MapPost handler parameter is a complex type (like Product), the framework reads JSON from the request body and deserializes it by default.",
  "REST 约定：创建成功返回 201 Created，并在 Location 头给出新资源的 URL。Results.Created 同时设置二者。": "REST convention: a successful create returns 201 Created with the new resource URL in the Location header. Results.Created sets both.",
  "用插值字符串拼 Location，例如 $\"/products/{product.Id}\"。": "Build the Location with an interpolated string, e.g. $\"/products/{product.Id}\".",
  "用 MapPost 映射 \"/products\"": "Map \"/products\" with MapPost",
